Package: onemap
Title: Construction of Genetic Maps in Experimental Crosses
Version: 3.2.2
Description: Analysis of molecular marker data from model and non-model
        systems. For the later, it allows statistical analysis by
        simultaneously estimating linkage and linkage phases (genetic
        map construction) according to Wu and colleagues (2002)
        <doi:10.1006/tpbi.2002.1577>. All analysis are based on
        multi-point approaches using hidden Markov models.
